  <p>Sets the wrap mode for all three coordinates of texture lookups on
this layer. This is equivalent to calling
<link xref="Cogl.Pipeline.set_layer_wrap_mode_s"/>,
<link xref="Cogl.Pipeline.set_layer_wrap_mode_t"/> and
<link xref="Cogl.Pipeline.set_layer_wrap_mode_p"/> separately.</p>
